Finally, the pipeline concludes by exporting the measured features of the segmented objects into a CSV file. This export step is important as it allows us to store our results in a structured format that can be easily accessed and analyzed. The CSV file not only serves as a data storage solution but also acts as a valuable resource for further research and analysis.

This pipeline ensures that your images are processed in a systematic and efficient manner, enabling you to extract valuable information about the objects within your images. By following these steps, you can effectively leverage the power of JIPipe to achieve your goals of segmentation, feature extraction, and data export. The structured approach taken here allows for the efficient handling of your images, resulting in a robust and effective image analysis pipeline that meets your needs.
